===message:Yes, TV might have reflected women's roles in the 1950s but not their attitudes about the roles.  In shows like "Leave it to Beaver" you never saw the mother bored.  TV gave women the idea that they were supposed to stay at home and like it, but I bet a great deal of them were not satisfied with doing just that.
