===message:I agree, tv seemed to glorify the stay at home mom.  She always seemed satisfied and happy to please everyone in the family.  We must remember that the tv executives at the time were men; they wanted to portray women as happy women who were content in their role as homemaker.  The tv wives provided role models of how a woman should feel and act.  But I do agree, I do not think that this role was satisfing to all women and that is one factor as to why women looked to work outside the home.
